Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.42,0:00:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.12,0:00:16.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的时候没给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.98,0:00:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点不合季节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很棒啊  海外旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.66,0:00:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.32,0:00:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候我们也去过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.72,0:00:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐完全想不起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:30.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.12,0:00:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像吃过附有冰淇淋的大薄饼和挤满奶油的香蕉派…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只记得这些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.27,0:00:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  走吧  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.72,0:02:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  吃饭咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:28.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（呐呐  进军海外吧！）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.15,0:02:35.15,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}番外篇　　计划！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.12,0:02:42.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  这边  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经帮你点了香蕉奶昔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晒黑的皮肤已经恢复了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.86,0:02:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:53.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新陈代谢简直跟婴儿差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有点年轻过头了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  这是给你的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:03:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～谢谢学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.10,0:03:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵的也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:10.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了  刚才的短信是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我们正商量着要去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:17.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是去海边  而是要去海外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说「进军海外」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过才刚去过夏日节啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:25.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还是应考生吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:27.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以考完才去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:29.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  毕业旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵也一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩会更开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  总之先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看指南手册  然后再商量下去哪儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏季讲习不是快开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然夏季讲习和考试复习两手都会抓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你看  人就是要有零食才会有干劲嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力过后总得吃点零食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.93,0:04:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是结束后有份期待的话  考试也就能熬过去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  你们只是想稍微逃避一下现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没逃啊  才没逃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上我还好好用功了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.86,0:04:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好  稍微想一下开心的事也好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连澪学姐也这样  感觉压力不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪儿好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多真不好选
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  只是计划一下的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽约…不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入浴？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:40.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「纽约」=ニューヨーク，「入浴」=ニュウヨク，日语发音相近）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯小姐  这呆装得真不怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啦没啦没啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽约是在美国吧  也就是吉太出生的国家咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:50.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太  这是你的家乡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太可能会很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是回老家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪学姐认为去哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:04:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我选英国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有种摇滚发源地的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  去看看演唱会  音乐剧什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英国也是红茶的发源地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  到海外去喝茶也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「英国」很像「蟋蟀」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:14.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「英国」=イギリス，「蟋蟀」=キリギリス）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就别来吐槽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么律认为哪里好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.51,0:05:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.79,0:05:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次到国外果然还是去夏威夷比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律选得也不怎么样嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天热的地方冰淇淋会特别好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威夷也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…学姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要大家一起的话我去哪里都行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.71,0:05:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:43.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  只要零食好吃的地方去哪里都行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.25,0:05:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个贪吃鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.41,0:05:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉大家意见完全不统一啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去我家别墅其实也可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芬兰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不错啊  好想看看极光
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  芬兰有「空气吉他大赛」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.98,0:06:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟吉太一起登场
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是空气吉他  所以用不着吉太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:11.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  也没必要急着决定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  各自再想下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海外旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  是小梓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪儿旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部的大家提到了毕业旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我也正计划着学生会的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.01,0:06:41.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想再去一次京都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前有很多想去却没去成的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻音部打算去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:50.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都想去海外
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩亨佐·达罗  吴哥窟  马丘比丘  都想去一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}摩亨佐·达罗：又称死丘，位于巴基斯坦南部的古代印度河流域文明大都会。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}吴哥窟：柬埔寨西北方庙宇，以建筑宏伟与浮雕细致闻名于世，也是世界上最大的庙宇。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:57.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}马丘比丘：位于秘鲁境内库斯科西北的印加遗迹，世界新七大奇迹之一。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马兹比丘？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:06:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马丘比丘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马丘比兹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不习惯的话确实挺难念的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉给我留了个面子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  忧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.69,0:07:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来买书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微给姐姐找点旅行用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来送麦茶…了…姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.38,0:07:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啊  我刚刚还在好好学习的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不骗你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  姐姐你们居然要去海外…我稍微有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:00.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么姐姐  这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望姐姐能够平安归来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也继续计划海外旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给小梓发下短信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.76,0:08:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先确定目的地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前还有一件要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在公园集合？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澪  被抓住的手的拇指向上  使劲挥出手刀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆脱后全速逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  梓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  你们在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防身术？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.58,0:08:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忧给我买的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.80,0:08:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果买了这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不浪费小忧的一番好意  大家正在实践
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵也学习一下比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来轮到和梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.12,0:09:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当被人从后面抱住的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把钱交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用加上演技吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得有临场感的话比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  用脚后跟踢的小腿后逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受益非浅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冰～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:39.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要注意的就是不要迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看地图应该就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说  但上次在京都不还是迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:46.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就问路人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家不会日语哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  你会说英语吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单的日常对话应该没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果跟走散了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那问题就大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么从现在开始禁止讲日语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要努力练习到即使不能说英语也能把意思传达清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  No日语
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「日语」本身就是日语吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where very delicious cake shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里有好吃的蛋糕店？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.09,0:10:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种话一般不会问吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般问的是观光胜地或能过夜的旅店之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where my hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里是我的旅店？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅店是你家开的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点怪  但能讲出旅店名字的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家就能帮我们指路了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.53,0:10:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「旅店」的英语也是Hotel吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发音互通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像按日语发音说「Wa—ter— please」对方未必能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印象中英语课上这么说过…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那该怎么讲才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是不要拉长  说「Water please」的话比较接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有水人会死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起说得半桶水的话  用肢体语言的话可能更好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也看不出是需要水啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个痛苦的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盂兰盆舞？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.30,0:11:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也是水  但形容「需要水」是不是太抽象了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是祈雨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:36.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「琴」与「事情」同音，所以唯表达的是「没什么好笑的」(笑いことじゃない)）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说小梓答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然答对了  但这也没什么意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.32,0:11:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且「琴」的意思外国人也不会懂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…感觉跟旅行扯得太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  话说回来大家都有护照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:11:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个不能用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  过期了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:11.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  反正大家都要去办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要的东西有身份证和户口本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有护照用照片和护照申请书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  未成年需要家长的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及身份证明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有手续费
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要这么多东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.44,0:12:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会帮姐姐准备齐全的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.40,0:12:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出国可真麻烦啊  忧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得应该有申请夏季讲习时候用过的照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  办护照穿校服的话有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份证明…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那学生手册应该就可以了吧  里面有学生证
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么后天  把需要的东西凑齐然后集合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:12:59.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（发送中）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:13:00.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（已发出）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没决定要出国
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和也去办一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.26,0:13:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等决定了再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.57,0:13:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:17.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和也是来办护照的？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么护照啊  我是来拍健身中心入会照片的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.16,0:13:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健身中心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:25.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和你要入会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你往哪儿看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还假装个什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个烦恼多多的年纪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.90,0:13:34.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您掉东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.06,0:13:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.94,0:13:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.12,0:13:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉稍微有点紧张…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再照一次吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要照啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:49.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  你们说护照…要去海外吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.84,0:13:50.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？去哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今未定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:14:01.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}彩色证件照  立等可取！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:14:01.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}出像清晰  重复拍照  护照专用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.86,0:14:01.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}另有亲切的语音向导功能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:58.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们好像计划着毕业旅行时候去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.49,0:14:01.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前先制定好应考复习计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和没去过海外吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然有  还是学生的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去过哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲绳？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  冲绳不算海外…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  撑撑面子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小佐和要不要一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次去海外是和学生们一起吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就度蜜月的时候去吧  小佐和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒啊  蜜月～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  全部凑齐  这就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:44.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（护照申请办理处）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,  谢谢你陪我们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家东西都带齐了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:14:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:14:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律你也带齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.45,0:15:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.37,0:15:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…学生手册忘带了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去拿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  叫聪送来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.67,0:15:24.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  聪  现在有空吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:30.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:31.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有发团扇的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说…也用不着到外边来等吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃冰淇淋…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办完再说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐真是的  下次注意点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.32,0:16:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:04.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律的弟弟是个怎么样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:09.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊…有点像小律吧  特别是眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小律男生版
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐真是的  下次注意点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:21.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个弟弟确实挺不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「姐姐真是的  下次注意点啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.99,0:16:29.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  要是唯学姐当弟弟的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}发证窗口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}填好申请书后，准备好申请文件排队办理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:33.74,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}照片由工作人员粘贴，请在窗口与申请书共同提交
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于能提交了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.61,0:16:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是秋山同学先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按学号来？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.03,0:16:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  下一位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  这张照片不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里必须要留有空白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.56,0:17:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为不知道上面有什么隐藏的东西  所以不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把头发扎起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得看起来会成熟一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为日本人到了国外看起来比较像小孩子的关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵这样的就跟小学生差不多？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯学姐不也是一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  重新照一张就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边有能拍证件照的机器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天用过  绝对没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:39.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把帘子拉上咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.44,0:17:43.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在画面上选择所需要的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会在证件照上出问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办个护照也不容易啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:56.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请做好准备后按下照相键
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为不容易才会更有喜悦感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很佩服你乐观向上的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:58.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍照会进行两次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:18:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,办好之后去吃冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那些东西就没有动力这点  我可不敢苟同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:05.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都害我笑出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始第二次拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.16,0:18:13.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用作护照的照片可能不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重拍了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍照会进行两次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:24.99,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:28.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得里面会很热
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:39.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始第二次拍摄  3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.81,0:18:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么会知道是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真是的  又成这样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于结束了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都怪谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.34,0:18:54.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:58.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正因如此  冰淇淋变得好吃极了～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对甜食还真是乐观向上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证件照到底拍了多少次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.10,0:19:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这要怎么处理…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留作纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.61,0:19:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.96,0:19:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.91,0:19:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过一星期左右还要再过来拿护照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.81,0:19:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等夏季讲习结束了再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我们到底准备去哪里旅行…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也得决定下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿好呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去英国看演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏威夷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡温泉打乒乓球如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用来办护照了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就去两次毕业旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到梓喵毕业的时候也去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我毕业的时候也是大家一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  英国  夏威夷  美国  温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都能去一遍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.58,0:20:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们哪里都可以去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.40,0:20:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  去看看海外旅行所需要的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:34.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发出发
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  充满海外旅行的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小律  小律
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.99,0:20:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.20,0:20:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了它的话  上课时候也能大睡特睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律需要这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为日本人必不可少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No rice, No life
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也需要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:21:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是钱被偷了  我们就在街头卖唱赚钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.59,0:21:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  海外出道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We are 「放学后茶会」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…好长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.77,0:21:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简称「HTT」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英语的话  不是应该是「After School Teatime」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不管到哪里都是「放学后茶会」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过旅行不能带上乐器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空气吉他  这是空气吉他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Believe的人就能看见！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那奇怪的说话方式还是省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:35.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定无论到哪儿都改不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  护照到手～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都能弄到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.91,0:21:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然比我先去海外…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.59,0:21:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小佐和也一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等到蜜月的时候会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来…我们要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.50,0:21:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到毕业的时候再说呗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是夏天嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前还有夏季讲习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No  夏季讲习…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.69,0:22:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会好好用功的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.74,0:22:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
